```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant F as Feature File
    participant D as defineFeature()
    participant A as API Route
    participant C as Components

    Dev->>F: Write students.feature.ts
    F->>D: defineFeature({ schema, permissions, ui })
    D->>D: Generate Drizzle Schema
    D->>D: Generate API Handlers
    D->>D: Generate Types
    D->>C: Generate FeatureDataGrid
    D->>C: Generate FeatureForm

    Note over A: Runtime Execution

    Client->>A: GET /api/resources/students
    A->>A: Check Permissions
    A->>A: Execute Query
    A-->>Client: JSON Response
```

