```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Student
    participant UI as Leave Form
    participant API as /api/leave
    participant DB as Database
    participant A as Admin
    participant N as Notification

    S->>UI: Request Leave
    UI->>API: POST /api/leave
    API->>DB: INSERT (status: pending)
    DB-->>API: Created
    API-->>S: Request submitted

    A->>API: GET /api/leave?status=pending
    API-->>A: Show pending requests

    A->>API: PATCH /api/leave/[id] {action: approve}
    API->>DB: UPDATE status=approved
    DB-->>API: Success
    API->>N: Send notification
    N-->>S: Leave approved!
```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Student
    participant UI as Journal Page
    participant API as /api/journal
    participant DB as users.settings (JSONB)

    S->>UI: Open Journal
    UI->>API: GET /api/journal
    API->>DB: Extract journalEntries
    DB-->>API: Return entries
    API-->>UI: Display entries

    S->>UI: New Entry
    UI->>UI: Check daily limit
    S->>API: POST /api/journal
    API->>API: Validate (one per day)
    API->>DB: Append to journalEntries
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>S: Entry created
```

